{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "058055d4-4680-4fd4-aeaa-3aa9f8300e28", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/058055d4-4680-4fd4-aeaa-3aa9f8300e28@8.pkg/1772597638580/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597638776", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/058055d4-4680-4fd4-aeaa-3aa9f8300e28@8.pkg/1772597638580/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597638776"}, "identifier": "058055d4-4680-4fd4-aeaa-3aa9f8300e28", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>审清题干</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>题干中明确提到 “我们是父母的子女，老师的学生；在小区里，我们是邻居；国外旅游遇到，我们都是中国人”，这清晰地展示了在家庭、学校、小区、国外等不同的社会环境中，“我们” 因为处于不同的社会关系里，而具有了不同的身份，如子女、学生、邻居、中国人等。因此B选项符合题意。A、D选项错误，C不符合题意。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<ol>\n\t<li>（原创）我们是父母的子女，老师的学生；在小区里，我们是邻居；国外旅游遇到，我们都是中国人。这表明（　　）</li>\n</ol>\n", "title": "（原创）我们是父母的子女，老师的学生；在小区里，我们是邻居；国外旅游遇到，我们都是中国人。这表明（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/058055d4-4680-4fd4-aeaa-3aa9f8300e28@8.pkg/item.json?v=1754580354053", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choic